$RAZV6_PTH
Raz [F:PTH]BPAINV
Raz [F:PTH]BPAPAY
Raz [F:PTH]BPOADD
Raz [F:PTH]BPOADDLIG
Raz [F:PTH]BPOCRY
Raz [F:PTH]BPOCRYNAM
Raz [F:PTH]BPOCTY
Raz [F:PTH]BPONAM
Raz [F:PTH]BPOPOSCOD
Raz [F:PTH]BPOSAT
Raz [F:PTH]BPRPAY
Raz [F:PTH]CCE
Raz [F:PTH]CPY
Raz [F:PTH]DEP
Raz [F:PTH]DIE
Raz [F:PTH]DSPVOU
Raz [F:PTH]DSPWEU
Raz [F:PTH]EECNUM
Raz [F:PTH]EECNUMDEB
Raz [F:PTH]FFWADD
Raz [F:PTH]ICTCTY
Raz [F:PTH]INVDTALIN1
Raz [F:PTH]INVDTALIN2
Raz [F:PTH]INVDTAVAT1
Raz [F:PTH]INVDTAVAT2
Raz [F:PTH]TOTAMTATI
Raz [F:PTH]TOTAMTATIL
Raz [F:PTH]TOTAMTNOT
Raz [F:PTH]TOTAMTNOTL
Raz [F:PTH]TOTLINAMT
Raz [F:PTH]TOTLINQTY
Raz [F:PTH]TOTLINVOU
Raz [F:PTH]TOTLINWEU
Raz [F:PTH]TOTTAXAMT
Raz [F:PTH]VACBPR
Raz [F:PTH]VACTYP
Raz [F:PTH]WRHE
Return
